<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ana ie Pa!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nawpna leh kipahna nanga,
 Ka nawpna leh ka kipahna;
 Aw Lal Isu nangmah nei piek ngei a hi.

[V2]
 Aw, a na ie pa, Kalvari tang,
 Na thawk nat zie ka en ngam puoi;
 Na thihna tuolthing!

[V3]
 2. Mipi tamtakin a deih puou,
 Israel chate'n a nawlhsau;
 Jentel Sapchuomte'n kalvari ah pawm ui.

[V4]
 3. Jentel Sapchuom I vangnei ngei,
 Lei a thilthawn piek chauh lo le;
 Hukdamna leh van Lallukhuk I chanbeh.
 4. Pienthakna thagau nang lo chun,
 Tung thei puong ie van gam nuom chu!
 Aw van Lal thagau thiengtho ei pui zelin.</lyrics>
<author>Ngulsang</author>
<hymn_number>80</hymn_number>
</song>